title: "forge-again"
abstract: >-
  A modernized fork of Stable Diffusion WebUI Forge, ported to Gradio 6,
  Python 3.12 and current PyTorch / HuggingFace releases, with a
  self-bootstrapping launcher and a built-in vision-LLM assistant.
